        <V n="text" t="single">
          <T n="single">0xB7A76236<!--String: "Those who live in the area, or visit frequently, have all sorts of stories to tell about the unusual creature they've seen skulking about in Crystal Valley. Some say it's benevolent...while others feel it's more malevolent. Many are torn as to whether or not it's even an actual bird, or something else entirely...though there's always a bit of a twinkle in the eye of locals when they joke about it.\n\nSome Sims tell stories about being lost and guided to safety by the creature, while others will tell stories about seeing a flurry of feathers as they're chased out of a prime fishing spot."--></T>
